<h3>
Programming Tools
</h3>

<p>

Throughout POE I programmed robots using VEXcode while learning Python and C++. As the year progressed, programming became less about syntax and more about solving engineering problems through logical thinking.

</p>

<ul>

<li>VEXcode</li>
<li>Python</li>
